🔹 3. PROJECT OVERVIEW
The RDSS 2.0 project focused on large-scale strengthening of power distribution infrastructure through transmission line development, substation expansion, and system integration across multiple locations.
G&D Brothers executed critical infrastructure components including transmission lines, transformers, substations, and feeder systems, ensuring seamless integration with existing electrical networks.

